# ── Local environment overrides for serverless-offline ──────────────────
# Copy this to .env.local and fill in your values.
# .env.local is gitignored — safe for secrets.
#
# The `dev` script already sources .env.local automatically via:
#   export $(cat .env.local 2>/dev/null | xargs)
# Just create the file with your vars and run `pnpm dev`.

# Telegram bot token (required for /telegram/process-bot-message)
# Get yours from @BotFather on Telegram.
# TELEGRAM_TOKEN=

# Optional in local, required in prod. Must match Telegram setWebhook secret_token.
# TELEGRAM_WEBHOOK_SECRET=

# Optional locally. When empty, transaction event publishing is disabled.
# TRANSACTION_EVENTS_QUEUE_URL=
# TRANSACTION_EVENTS_QUEUE_ARN=
